<P>
Hahn's Muddy Encounter: Jessica Hahn, the former church secretary whose sexual 
encounter with television evangelist Jim Bakker started the downfall of his PTL 
empire, will be hosting a pay-TV special Nov. 10 that features heavy-metal rock 
and female mud wrestling. "It's not 'Masterpiece Theater.' It's a little 
crazy," Hahn says of the show, "Thunder and Mud." "I've got mud in front of me 
and heavy metal behind me. The girls all look great -- I felt like their 
grandmother." Asked if her rock and mud show is denigrating to women, Hahn, 30, 
