<P>
Photo, Carl Strong has resigned as Torrance High's basketball coach. DEBORA 
GOODIER / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Eric Hansen, here catching a pass in a 
summer league, has caught 72 in eight games this season to pace the Saxons' 
offense. TODD ROSENBERG / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
