EAST GERMANY -- GOVERNMENT; GOVERNMENT REFORM; EAST GERMANY -- POLITICS; 
DEMONSTRATIONS -- EAST GERMANY; SOCIALISM; REUNIFICATION; EAST GERMANY -- 
