FREEWAYS; PROPERTY DAMAGE; NIMITZ FREEWAY; NORTHERN CALIFORNIA -- 
TRANSPORTATION; SAN FRANCISCO -- TRANSPORTATION; EARTHQUAKE SAFETY; CALIFORNIA 
